name: CD - Dear Diary (2010-Red Light Records)
description:
Rock One : 8/10
French Metal : 17/20

Recorded & mixed at Warmaudio, Décines - France (Uncommonmenfrommars, Flying Donuts…) and mastered at New Alliance East Studio in Cambridge - USA (The Ghost Of A Thousand, Cave In, Against Me!, The Unseen, Terror, Isis, Converge…).

In the vein of The Bled, Raised Fist, The Ghost Of A Thousand, Cancer Bats or Comeback Kid...
